    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis represents a rare, preserved example of Mazda\u2019s sequential twin-turbocharged engineering. The 13B-REW rotary engine exhibits exceptional compression across both rotors, maintaining factory-spec boost pressure through the complex vacuum system. Power is delivered via a precise five-speed manual gearbox to a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The double-wishbone suspension remains tight and responsive, retaining its legendary 50/50 weight distribution. This survivor features original paint with zero oxidation and an immaculate interior free of typical bolster wear or UV damage. A mechanically pristine, investment-grade vehicle for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
