    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly remarkable, museum-quality vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in pristine, showroom condition, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and shielded from the elements since its original purchase. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like finish with zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks, further protected by a top-tier ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains soft and supple with no creasing or bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by original factory mats since day one. Every technological feature, sensor, and button operates with the precision of a new vehicle. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It comes with a binder of exhaustive service records performed exclusively by master technicians, ensuring the engine and transmission operate in perfect harmony. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, and the vehicle sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires. For the buyer who demands perfection and a vehicle that drives exactly as it did when it first left the assembly line, this is the definitive choice.",
